{
  "info": {
    "name": "SysFeedback - Tech Challenge Fase 4 (Grupo 18)",
    "description": "Collection com todos os endpoints da API SysFeedback.\n\nFluxo sugerido:\n1. Auth > Login (ALUNO/PROFESSOR/ADMIN) — o token é salvo automaticamente na variável {{token}}.\n2. Chame os demais endpoints — o header Authorization: Bearer {{token}} é herdado.\n\nUsuários do seed (senha 123456): aluno@fiap.com, professor@fiap.com, admin@fiap.com.\n\nRegras de autorização:\n- POST /avaliacoes -> ALUNO\n- GET /avaliacoes, GET/POST /feedback -> PROFESSOR ou ADMIN\n- /users (POST, GET, DELETE) -> ADMIN | PUT /users -> autenticado\n- POST /internal/relatorio/semanal -> header X-Internal-Api-Key",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "internalApiKey", "value": "chave-local-123", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Registrar (novo usuário)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Novo Aluno\",\n  \"email\": \"novo.aluno@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\",\n  \"role\": \"ALUNO\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/registrar",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "registrar"]
            },
            "description": "Registra um usuário. Roles válidas: ADMIN, PROFESSOR, ALUNO. Use um e-mail que ainda não exista (os do seed já estão criados)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (ALUNO)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
                  "    console.log('Token ALUNO salvo em {{token}}');",
                  "} else { console.log('Login falhou:', pm.response.code); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"aluno@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica como ALUNO e grava o token em {{token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (PROFESSOR)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
                  "    console.log('Token PROFESSOR salvo em {{token}}');",
                  "} else { console.log('Login falhou:', pm.response.code); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"professor@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica como PROFESSOR e grava o token em {{token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (ADMIN)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', pm.response.json().token);",
                  "    console.log('Token ADMIN salvo em {{token}}');",
                  "} else { console.log('Login falhou:', pm.response.code); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica como ADMIN e grava o token em {{token}}."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar usuário (ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Novo Professor\",\n  \"email\": \"novo.professor@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"123456\",\n  \"role\": \"PROFESSOR\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["users"] },
            "description": "Requer role ADMIN (faça Login (ADMIN) antes)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar usuários (ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["users"] },
            "description": "Requer role ADMIN."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Buscar por email (ADMIN/PROFESSOR)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/email/aluno@fiap.com",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "email", "aluno@fiap.com"]
            },
            "description": "Requer role ADMIN ou PROFESSOR."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar usuário (autenticado)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Aluno Atualizado\",\n  \"email\": \"aluno@fiap.com\",\n  \"password\": \"novaSenha123\",\n  \"role\": \"ALUNO\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Requer usuário autenticado. Defina {{userId}} com o id retornado na listagem."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Deletar usuário (ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Requer role ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Avaliacoes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Criar avaliação (ALUNO)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"descricao\": \"A aula estava confusa e sem exemplos praticos\",\n  \"nota\": 2\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["avaliacoes"] },
            "description": "Requer role ALUNO. A urgencia e derivada da nota (0-3 ALTA, 4-6 MEDIA, 7-10 BAIXA). Faca Login (ALUNO) antes."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar avaliações (PROFESSOR/ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/avaliacoes", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["avaliacoes"] },
            "description": "Requer role PROFESSOR ou ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Feedback",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Gerar feedback do período (PROFESSOR/ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"inicio\": \"2026-07-01T00:00:00\",\n  \"fim\": \"2026-07-31T23:59:59\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/feedback", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["feedback"] },
            "description": "Requer role PROFESSOR ou ADMIN. Gera e persiste o consolidado do periodo."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar feedbacks gerados (PROFESSOR/ADMIN)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/feedback", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["feedback"] },
            "description": "Requer role PROFESSOR ou ADMIN."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Interno (máquina-a-máquina)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Relatório semanal (API key)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "X-Internal-Api-Key", "value": "{{internalApiKey}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/internal/relatorio/semanal",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["internal", "relatorio", "semanal"]
            },
            "description": "Endpoint consumido pela Cloud Function relatorio-semanal. Protegido por API key (header X-Internal-Api-Key = {{internalApiKey}}), sem JWT. Sem parâmetros considera os últimos 7 dias. Retorna média, contagens por dia/urgência e a lista de avaliações."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
